OL,3,CPubs can open until 5am on Monday for
OL,4,CEngland v Mexico in World Cup
OL,6,FA pub in West Cumbria is so excited
OL,7,Fthey can bring World Cup fever to
OL,8,Ftheir customers, the landlord has
OL,9,Fenlisted the support of a local goat
OL,10,Fto cheer on England.
OL,12,FEngland play Mexico in Mexico City at
OL,13,F1am UK time on Monday in their round-
OL,14,Fof-16 match.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
