CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783691326
OL,3,CPubs can open until 5am on Monday for
OL,4,CEngland v Mexico in World Cup
OL,6,FThe Government had initially said
OL,7,Flicensing laws would not be relaxed
OL,8,Fbut on Thursday a U-turn saw Prime
OL,9,FMinister Keir Starmer announce pubs in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales could stay open
OL,11,Funtil 5am, saying "Football might be
OL,12,Fcoming home but we're making sure fans
OL,13,Fdon't have to".
OL,15,FBusinesses have welcomed the news
OL,16,Fsaying it will now boost local
OL,17,Feconomies.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783691326
OL,3,CPubs can open until 5am on Monday for
OL,4,CEngland v Mexico in World Cup
OL,6,FThe Landlord of the Lion and the Lamb
OL,7,Fin Gosforth, Richard Mawson, says
OL,8,Ffinances have been really difficult
OL,9,Ffor pubs with all bills going up and
OL,10,Ffootfall going down. He says the whole
OL,11,FWorld Cup tournament has made a big
OL,12,Fdifference because it has been "so
OL,13,Fbusy and so well supported".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783691326
OL,3,CPubs can open until 5am on Monday for
OL,4,CEngland v Mexico in World Cup
OL,6,FHowever, Mr Mawson says he had
OL,7,Finitially been told it was too late to
OL,8,Fapply for a special late-opening
OL,9,Flicense, after waiting until England
OL,10,Fqualified before incurring the expense
OL,11,Fof applying. He told ITV Border, "so
OL,12,Fmy world fell apart because I'd let
OL,13,Fall our customers down by not getting
OL,14,Fthe license in earlier."
OL,16,FNow he says the U-turn "means
OL,17,Feverything" so they're getting the pub
OL,18,Fready for the big night with a very
OL,19,Fspecial guest, he says "just makes
OL,20,Fpeople smile".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
