OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783691326
OL,3,CPubs can open until 5am on Monday for
OL,4,CEngland v Mexico in World Cup
OL,6,FTongo the goat is already sporting his
OL,7,FEngland jersey, but he has a curious
OL,8,Fname for the occasion. In Spanish
OL,9,Fslang, the language of the host
OL,10,Fcountry Mexico, 'Tongo' means a
OL,11,F'sporting fraud, fix or deception',
OL,12,Fbut in Polynesian culture it also
OL,13,Frefers to the red mangrove tree. Fans
OL,14,Fwill no doubt be hoping for a clean
OL,15,Fgame where the red and white team is
OL,16,Fvictorious.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
