FL,327,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F326A1783691326
OL,3,CPubs can open until 5am on Monday for
OL,4,CEngland v Mexico in World Cup
OL,6,FThe Landlord says even though the
OL,7,Fmatch is on overnight, he expects the
OL,8,Fpub will still be busy, but he will be
OL,9,Fhoping to "keep the noise down for the
OL,10,Fneighbours" and he believes in
OL,11,FEngland, telling ITV Border "they're
OL,12,Fthe best in the business, there's no
OL,13,Freason they can't score one more goal
OL,14,Fthan the opposition."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/6
